data.description: This completely renovated Cutler Bay 4/2 Single Family Home with an Added Efficiency Unit attached, is a Must See.  This Home has a Bright and Light Open Feel, a Brand-New Modern Kitchen with a Large Island, new Stainless-Steel Appliances,  new Washer/Dryer, New Roof (2 months old) with a 25-year warranty, Impact Windows with Lifetime Guarantee, Two Exterior Gazebos, Beautiful Tile Flooring throughout, Spacious Renovated Bedrooms, Updated Bathrooms, Plenty of Storage Space, and Enough Room to Park Your Boat or RV.  This home was recently Painted in Neutral Colors that beautifies and enhances its curb appeal.  The home also features an Amazing Yard with Space for a Pool.  Nothing left to do but Move In! a Must See and the best of all, No Association at all!
